# Patched ANTLR Go codegen templates (ANTLR 4.13.2 Go.stg + yaklang patches).

# Diff vs upstream jar Go.stg:
# 1) github.com/antlr4-go/antlr/v4 -> github.com/yaklang/antlr/v4 (6 places)
# 2) Restore 4.11.x "this := receiver" aliases in RuleActionFunction,
#    RuleSempredFunction, RuleFunction, and LeftRecursiveRuleFunction.
#    Upstream 4.13.2 dropped these, but grammars still use Java-style "this"
#    in actions/predicates (antlr/antlr4#4311 / grammars-v4#2177).
#
# Do not invoke java -cp here directly from language scripts.
# Use: common/yak/antlr4util/antlr4
